---
group_count: 13
atr1_unknown: 4
entries:
  After00:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 13
      - text: "你知道那座像城堡的建築物\n是什麼東西嗎？"
  After01:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 12
      - text: 憑我的實力，只能到此為止嗎……
  After02:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 24
      - text: 它名為
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 阿卡萊堡壘
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "，\n是在很久以前，海拉魯王國還健在時……\n為守護這個阿卡萊地區而建造的，\n因此又被稱為「堅不可摧的堡壘」。\n據說在那場大災厄中，海拉魯城堡遭到燒毀，\n海拉魯軍隊失去國王和公主後\n實在無計可施……便以這裡為據點，\n持續做最後的抵抗。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound2
          unknown:
            - 10
            - 205
      - text: "但是，失控的守護者展開了猛烈攻擊，\n堡壘根本無法抵擋，結果還是失陷……\n換句話說，這裡是\n海拉魯王國滅亡前的最後一塊土地。"
  After02_2:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 17
      - text: "聽說我的祖先也是死在這裡。\n所以我為了弔唁祂們而來到這裡……\n但只要守護者還在活動，\n似乎就只能前進到此……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 12
      - text: "聽說挺身對抗守護者的人，\n沒有一個倖存……\n雖然你看起來不像有勇無謀的傢伙，\n如果要前往堡壘，可千萬要小心啊！"
  After03:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 16
      - text: "只要看著這座巨大的建築物，\n還有變成廢墟的小鎮……\n就能感受到以前的海拉魯王國\n有多麼繁榮呢。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 13
      - text: 其實我很想再靠近一點欣賞，但是……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n如果你要前往堡壘，可千萬要小心喔！"
  Atacked00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 2
            - 14
      - text: 可惡，這種地方居然有怪物！
  Atacked01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 2
            - 14
      - text: 怎麼了？放馬過來啊！
  Failed00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: 我也真是的……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n居然讓你看到這麼難看的樣子。\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: 同為旅行者，我就給你個忠告吧。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n千萬別小看怪物啊。"
  Failed01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: "我也真是的，太大意了……\n\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: 城堡看得太入迷，一不小心就被打倒了。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
      - text: "\n你也要當心自己的背後喔。"
  GoodBye00:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 12
      - text: "我是為了前往那座堡壘，才來到這裡的。\n儘管我好不容易才來到這裡，但是……"
  Guardian00:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 8
            - 14
      - text: 可惡的守護者！
  Near00:
    attributes: Npc_Attacked_012
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound2
          unknown:
            - 13
            - 205
      - text: 可惡……只能到此為止嗎？
  SavedLv1_00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 17
      - text: 呼……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n給你添麻煩了……\n雖然我自己就能解決那種傢伙了，\n但還是給你點謝禮，拿去吧。"
  SavedLv1_01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 15
      - text: 啐……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n多管閒事……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: "雖然我自己就能解決那種傢伙了，\n但還是得給你謝禮才行！拿去吧。"
  SavedLv2_00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 3
            - 13
      - text: 唔……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n看來你救了我……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: "雖然剛才的怪物我應該也能解決，\n但還是給你點謝禮吧。"
  SavedLv2_01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 18
      - text: ……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n得救了……\n剛才的怪物還挺棘手的。\n讓我向你道個謝吧。"
  SavedLv3_00:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 9
            - 0
      - text: 抱……抱歉……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n老實說，剛才的怪物非常危險，\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: "儘管我對自己的劍術也有信心……\n這是謝禮，你就收下吧！"
  SavedLv3_01:
    attributes: ""
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 4
            - 8
      - text: 你真厲害啊……
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n居然這麼輕鬆就把我難以對付的怪物……\n"
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: "你應該不是普通人吧？\n讓我向你道個謝吧。"
